  "texts": [
    "Absence of checks on algorithmic demotion (Code: RA) elevates private economic calculations over considerations of expressive diversity and exposure plurality.",
    "This prioritizes efficiency over ethics.",
    "Oversight and due process are needed for any restrictions on legal speech [96,161].Truth Judgments and Shared Liability Compelled counterspeech and warnings on otherwise legal content creates tensions with liberties of conscience and freedom of uncoerced thought.",
    "Safeguards should be strengthened for only employing this extra speech as a last resort based on judicial review [31,181].",
    "Similarly, restrictions based on opaque judgements of truthfulness and potential virality, rather than direct incitement standards, contradict assumptions behind epistemic rights and the \"marketplace of ideas.\""
